- Test Case #1: Concatenating two strings
Description: Adding together two strings
Result: Both strings concatenated together

- Test Case #2: Reverse a string
Description: Revsering a string's order
Result: The string's order was reversed, however, only one of the strings "ruben" reversed, "plascencia" did not

- Test Case #3: Uppercasing a string
Description: Transforms a string's letters to be completely uppercase
Result: It expected "plascencia" as an input, but the result was "RUBEN" as the output

- Test Case #4: Trimming whitespace
Description: To trim the whitespace around a given string
Result: Trimmed down the whitespace and trailing around the string and displayed a normal string output
